# Prerequisites

- You're on a Mac
- You have administrative rights on your machine
- You have an App Store account
- You've upgrade to [El Capitan](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/os-x-el-capitan/id1018109117) from the App Store
- You've installed [XCode 7 from the App Store](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/xcode/id497799835) or [Downloads for Apple Developers](https://developer.apple.com/downloads/)

