# The XCode License

## Agree To It

XCode is an application that lets you build iOS applications. It also provides a lot of  tools for building all sorts of other applications.

- Open Spotlight (⌘ Space), type `terminal` and press Return
- In the Terminal window that pops up, type the following: `sudo xcodebuild -license`
- It will ask for your password (the one you log into your computer with)
- Press `q` to jump to the end of the license
- Type `agree` and press return to agree to the license

