# Stop using the Mouse

## To resize windows

Use [ShiftIt](https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt) to move and resize windows using the keyboard.

```sh
brew cask install shiftit
```

Then use Spotlight to start ShiftIt.

---

# Giving ShiftIt Permissions

ShiftIt needs permission to control your computer. Let's give it that permission.

1. Go to System Preferences > Security & Privacy > Privacy > Accessibility
1. Click the lock to make changes (bottom-left corner) and enter your password
1. In the right-hand pane called "Allow the apps below to control your computer." and check "ShiftIt"
1. Start ShiftIt, it should work without any issue.

These instructions come from <https://github.com/fikovnik/ShiftIt/issues/110#issuecomment-20834932>

